│ provides methods to manipulate incoming values and blocks, such as `addIncoming`,       │
│ `removeIncomingValue`, and `replaceIncomingBlockWith`. These methods are crucial for    │
│ maintaining the structural integrity of PHI nodes during transformations.               │
│                                                                                         │
