│ To fix this, we need to ensure that all PHINodes in the `exit` block are updated to     │
│ match the new loop structure. This can be achieved by iterating over the PHINodes in    │
│ the `exit` block and using methods like `addIncoming` or `replaceIncomingBlockWith` to  │
│ adjust their incoming values and blocks.                                                │
│                                                                                         │
